This script exports a joined table from SMDB with meta data relevant for the Butterfly.
You need to provide a password to access the database. This is done by setting the environment 
variable `PGPASSWORD` before running the script.

Example usage:   
PGPASSWORD='5J8DhII0RRsPW1' python /var/meta_db_apps/gg-metadatabase-ui/scripts/data_getters/butterfly/meta_data_getter.py --output path/to/your/output_dir/output.tsv

Use --help to see all available options

See requirements.txt for dependencies.